      "message": "This stuff still needs to go.  In general, we don\u0027t want to be downloading things inside of scripts running on the bots; those steps belong in the recipe, or we ensure that the dependencies get isolated or delivered via CIPD.  And we definitely don\u0027t want to be messing with git in these scripts; the bot code has already gotten us into the correct state, so doing more here can only hurt.",
